{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 9094263}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por resoluci&#xF3;n exenta N&#xBA; 3.945, de 30 de diciembre de 2010, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, la distribuci&#xF3;n de la fracci&#xF3;n artesanal de la pesquer&#xED;a artesanales de Merluza com&#xFA;n Merluccius gayi correspondiente al &#xC1;rea Centro de la V Regi&#xF3;n, sometida al R&#xE9;gimen Artesanal de Extracci&#xF3;n por organizaciones de pescadores artesanales, para el per&#xED;odo enero-julio de 2011, expresada en toneladas, se efectuar&#xE1; de la siguiente manera:</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">Organizaciones de la V </div><div class=\"p\">Regi&#xF3;n Centro&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  R.S.U.&nbsp; &nbsp; Ene-Jun (ton) Julio </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (ton)</div><div class=\"p\">STI Pescadores Artesanales </div><div class=\"p\">de Caleta Diego Portales </div><div class=\"p\">de Valpara&#xED;so&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 05.01.037&nbsp;  985,147&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 65,676</div><div class=\"p\">STI Pesc. Art. de Conc&#xF3;n&nbsp; &nbsp;  05.06.043&nbsp;  169,853&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 11,324</div><div class=\"p\">No asociados (cuota residual)&nbsp; -&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  732,255&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 48,817</div><br><div class=\"p\">Total&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1.887,254&nbsp; &nbsp;  125,817</div><br></div>", "i": 9094264}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Valpara&#xED;so, 30 de diciembre de 2010.- Pablo Galilea Carrillo, Subsecretario de Pesca.</div></div>", "i": 9094265}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos